{"tid":2487761,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人以前睇死「全民造星」唔會成功","createTime":"2021-04-13T21:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T00:57:11.000Z","uid":110613,"like":121,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f0758e29c10250cc1de828a06b9f84be8091197c","tid":2487761,"uid":110613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T21:04:52.000Z","msg":"以前覺得參選者一係好mk一係抄韓星<br />\n個個冇星味，表演又尷尬<br />\n入面根本無所謂既「偶像」<br />\n選完都好，香港人一兩個月之後就唔會記得<br />\n<br />\n今日覺得固步自封既人係自己<br />\n點解去到2021年<br />\n以為哥哥、梅姐呢種先係合格既「星味」，先夠料做明星、上電視<br />\n的確呢班男仔仲係原石，某啲位表現仲係好尷尬，勝在性情夠貼地，相信會為香港電視節目定下新標準<br />\n<br />\n以前睇死香港出產男團<br />\n覺得日韓明星係香港出道都會變mk pop<br />\n但而家我覺得港星夠料fight低韓星、向東南亞發展<br />\n<br />\n好似奧運咁，好想向國際炫耀我地香港都有男團<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n恭喜姜濤接廣告接到手軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩肌研水、咩HPV、咩奇異果洗頭水<br />\n<span class=\"small\">係呀廣告商我地睇到架</span><br />\n仲愈黎愈多人識Error 同 Mirror<br />\n<span class=\"small\">（真係多謝晒CCTVB）</span><br />\n<br />\n期待mirror error以外既男團誕生"},{"pid":"a66e7bf703f8ed72114f18746d93c8584bff1746","tid":2487761,"uid":209773,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T21:06:14.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗住個節目係俾人笑吓"},{"pid":"5c6b850e74a9c59fd0eda80a6687d7a014785bae","tid":2487761,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T21:07:14.000Z","msg":"點知佢會食正tvb條水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f242c86b988ea9df40b77216463447f69e850fed","tid":2487761,"uid":2676,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T21:08:21.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得有幾個仲靚仔過姜濤，唱歌又咬字唔正<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解佢係最紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c98f3f9db7f24f1cb603313eb3e37b1edbe1f4e","tid":2487761,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a66e7bf703f8ed72114f18746d93c8584bff1746","tid":248